<template lang="pug">
.dashboard
  h2 kek
  mdc-button(raised, @click="logout") Logout
</template>

<script>
export default {
  name: "Dashboard",
  data() {
    return { pages: [], showModal: false, newPage: "", fetching: false };
  },
  created() {
    const token = this.$auth.token;
    // Call api function to get current pages
    this.fetching = true;
    this.$api("/pages", {body: {token}})
    .then(pages => {
      this.fetching = false;
      this.pages = pages;
    })
    .catch(ex => this.$toast.error("Fetch unsuccessful!", ex.message));
  },
  methods: {
    addPage(e, action) {
      let page = this.newPage;

      if(page && action === "approve") {
        if(page[0] !== "/") {
          page = `/${page}`;w
        }

        // Prevent duplicates
        if(!this.pages.includes(page)) {
          this.$router.push(`edit${page}`);
        } else {
          this.$toast.error("Sidfel", "Kunde inte lägga till den sidan för den finns redan!")
        }

        this.newPage = "";
      }
      this.showModal = false;
    },
    removePage(e, page) {
      e.stopPropagation();
      const index = this.pages.indexOf(page);
      const token = this.$auth.token;

      // Call api function to remove the page
      this.$api(`/pages${page}`, {method: "delete", body: { token }})
      .then(() => {
        this.$toast.success("Succé", `Sidan '${page}' har tagits bort.`);
        this.pages.splice(index, 1);
      })
      .catch(ex => this.$toast.error("Fetch unsuccessful!", ex.message));
    },
    logout(e) {
      this.$auth.logout();
      this.$router.push("/login");
    },
    changePassword(e) {
      e.preventDefault();
      const {password, verify} = e.target.elements;
      const {value} = password;

      if(value === verify.value) {
        this.$auth.changePassword(value).then(() => {
          this.$toast.success("Ändring lyckades", "Lösenordet har ändrats");
        }).catch(ex => {
          this.$toast.error(ex.header, ex.message);
        });
      } else {
        this.$toast.warning("Verifieringsfel", "Båda fälten måste vara likadana");
      }
    }
  }
};
</script>
